<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.3, maximum-scale=3.0, minimum-scale=0.85">


<title>
	City of Winds and Idylls - Disc 1: City of Winds and Idylls｜Genshin Impact - Repeat in a loop
</title><meta name="description" content="Type &#39;repeater&#39; between &#39;youtube&#39; and &#39;.com&#39; and your video will automatically repeat/replay in a loop.  Use a mini player without menus or toolbars.  Check top repeated videos.">
